<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>ApexRider - Own the Apex</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    /* General Reset */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background-color: #0d0d0d;
      color: #f0f0f0;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    header {
      background-color: #101010;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 50px 20px;
      border-bottom: 4px solid #00e0ff;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 3em;
      color: #00e0ff;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    header p {
      color: #cccccc;
      font-size: 1.2em;
    }

    .hero {
      background: url('https://your-image-url.com/apexrider.jpg') no-repeat center center/cover;
      height: 500px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .hero h2 {
      background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
      padding: 20px 40px;
      font-size: 2.5em;
      border: 2px solid #00e0ff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .content {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 60px auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .content h2 {
      font-size: 2em;
      color: #00e0ff;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .content p {
      font-size: 1.1em;
      color: #bbbbbb;
    }

    .features {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 30px;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    .feature-box {
      background-color: #1a1a1a;
      padding: 20px;
      border-left: 5px solid #00e0ff;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .feature-box h3 {
      color: #00e0ff;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .feature-box p {
      color: #cccccc;
    }

    footer {
      background-color: #101010;
      color: #777;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px;
      margin-top: 60px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h1>ApexRider</h1>
  <p>Precision Engineered for the Apex</p>
</header>

<section class="hero">
  <h2>Fast. Sharp. Unstoppable.</h2>
</section>

<section class="content">
  <h2>About ApexRider</h2>
  <p>
    The ApexRider is a machine built for those who command corners and dominate straightaways. 
    Crafted with aerodynamic precision and powered by a high-revving inline engine, it's the 
    ultimate expression of speed, style, and advanced control. From the racetrack to the streets, 
    ApexRider leads â€” others follow.
  </p>

  <div class="features">
    <div class="feature-box">
      <h3>Engine</h3>
      <p>999cc Liquid-Cooled Inline-4 with Crossplane Crankshaft</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-box">
      <h3>Top Speed</h3>
      <p>205 mph / 330 km/h</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-box">
      <h3>Ride Modes</h3>
      <p>Track | Sport | Rain | Custom</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-box">
      <h3>Electronics</h3>
      <p>Cornering ABS, Traction Control, Quickshifter, Launch Control</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  &copy; 2025 ApexRider Performance Division. All rights reserved.
</footer>

</body>
</html>
